text: Eric Russell Hutchinson (born 19 June 1965) is a former Australian politician. He represented the Division of Lyons in the Australian House of Representatives from September 2013 to July 2016 as a member of the Liberal Party of Australia. He is the Administrator of Norfolk Island since April 2017. ==References== Category:1965 births Category:Living people Category:Administrators of Norfolk Island
